479
00:48:08,413 --> 00:48:16,417
[SPEAKER_11]: for comments on these determination, the legal determination for the benefits of a project labor agreement.

480
00:48:16,998 --> 00:48:19,939
[SPEAKER_11]: I've been president of the Massachusetts Building Trades since 2007.

481
00:48:20,580 --> 00:48:28,664
[SPEAKER_11]: I've negotiated dozens and dozens of these agreements, everything from offshore wind to power plants to school construction.

482
00:48:29,784 --> 00:48:33,727
[SPEAKER_11]: This will clearly benefit the city of Medford and its residents.

483
00:48:34,167 --> 00:48:38,269
[SPEAKER_11]: You'll get a quality project completed on time and on budget.

484
00:48:39,270 --> 00:48:43,791
[SPEAKER_11]: I know we just heard a discussion about uncertainties on budgets.

485
00:48:44,331 --> 00:48:49,792
[SPEAKER_11]: One of the main benefits in relation to that conversation is you take a lot of uncertainty.

486
00:48:50,532 --> 00:48:52,512
[SPEAKER_11]: There are no strike, no lockout provisions.

487
00:48:52,972 --> 00:48:59,894
[SPEAKER_11]: You make sure that you have properly licensed people, Medford residents, for opportunities to work on this project.

488
00:49:00,354 --> 00:49:07,355
