739
01:12:06,537 --> 01:12:16,446
[SPEAKER_03]: I think even hearing you talk through the process of what you started doing in February and laying that out was helpful for, this is a new piece for me as well.

740
01:12:16,566 --> 01:12:21,870
[SPEAKER_03]: So I think certainly at the next Committee of the Whole if it's possible just to lay that out as well.

741
01:12:23,311 --> 01:12:27,253
[SPEAKER_03]: the diagrams as well, get a better sense of what exactly we're talking about.

742
01:12:27,274 --> 01:12:36,879
[SPEAKER_03]: I think that will help us, help the public understand and just, you know, moving forward be able to help us make some better and quicker decisions on it moving forward.

743
01:12:36,939 --> 01:12:43,963
[SPEAKER_03]: But yeah, just even have the outline of the process timeline before and then hopefully even afterwards what happens too just so that we kind of know full circle.

744
01:12:44,323 --> 01:12:45,383
[SPEAKER_03]: I think that would be very helpful.

745
01:12:45,744 --> 01:12:46,424
[SPEAKER_03]: So, thank you.

746
01:12:47,665 --> 01:12:47,945
[SPEAKER_03]: Thank you.

