01:13:30,610 --> 01:13:31,170
[SPEAKER_07]: Yeah.

755
01:13:31,230 --> 01:13:41,013
[SPEAKER_07]: So, you know, those are just some kind of things that I think will just help us to clarify, you know, because some of these are small, it looks like some of them are, you know, 10 square feet.

756
