[SPEAKER_07]: And then some are over 1,000 square feet.

757
01:13:44,855 --> 01:13:48,176
[SPEAKER_07]: So, I think that kind of descriptive

758
01:13:49,042 --> 01:13:54,011
[SPEAKER_07]: you know, just being able to like kind of show a little bit more other than just specifically the right-of-way plan would help too.

