01:15:17,333 --> 01:15:17,713
[SPEAKER_07]: Thank you.

776
01:15:20,337 --> 01:15:29,680
[SPEAKER_07]: All right, I will go to members of the public who would like to speak on the proposed orders of taking for the Mystic Avenue and Main Street.

777
01:15:30,140 --> 01:15:37,202
