830
01:19:43,131 --> 01:19:47,974
[SPEAKER_07]: So yes, just if I will recognize you, I'm sorry.

831
01:19:48,154 --> 01:19:50,296
[SPEAKER_07]: Thank you.

832
01:19:50,396 --> 01:19:52,658
[SPEAKER_21]: It sounds so easy, like you said, but

833
