[SPEAKER_21]: I think that an hour before this meeting, we had three of the eight members that are being affected reached out.

834
01:20:01,295 --> 01:20:08,240
[SPEAKER_21]: So this simple sliver of land to them might be to you, Owen, something simple.

835
01:20:08,300 --> 01:20:13,384
[SPEAKER_21]: But to them, talking to them is pretty life changing.

836
01:20:13,524 --> 01:20:22,390
[SPEAKER_21]: So I think that really having a better outline and really a better way to inform them and inform us as a council so we're prepared for that.

837
01:20:22,895 --> 01:20:23,896
[SPEAKER_21]: I think would have been helpful.

838
01:20:23,976 --> 01:20:25,437
[SPEAKER_21]: So I appreciate it.

839
01:20:25,637 --> 01:20:25,977
[SPEAKER_21]: Thank you.

