[SPEAKER_07]: Owen, if you'd like to speak.

842
01:20:34,842 --> 01:20:44,268
[SPEAKER_16]: You know, we have been reaching out to all these people and they are all aware of the land that was being asked for as an easement.

843
01:20:47,690 --> 01:20:47,930
[SPEAKER_07]: All right.

844
01:20:48,130 --> 01:20:48,651
[SPEAKER_07]: Thank you.

