01:25:53,817 --> 01:25:55,658
[SPEAKER_07]: Seeing none, any further discussion by members of the council?

903
01:25:58,274 --> 01:26:11,027
[SPEAKER_07]: Is there a motion to table, motion to table to the July 14th regular meeting, maybe a Committee of the Whole on, we'll figure out if we need a Committee of the Whole, but motion to table the July 14th regular meeting by Councilor Scarpelli, seconded by Councilor Callahan.

904
01:26:11,087 --> 01:26:11,968
[SPEAKER_07]: Motion is undebatable.

905
01:26:12,008 --> 01:26:12,929
[SPEAKER_07]: Mr. Clerk, please call the roll.

