01:34:45,853 --> 01:34:46,573
[SPEAKER_07]: Councilor Callahan.

992
01:34:49,743 --> 01:34:59,776
[SPEAKER_14]: I was just looking back at the original paper in February that was requesting information, and I think what's particularly been missing is

