1561
02:27:25,740 --> 02:27:26,400
[SPEAKER_19]: Councilor Lemming?

1562
02:27:26,961 --> 02:27:27,261
[SPEAKER_20]: Yes.

1563
02:27:28,501 --> 02:27:29,042
[SPEAKER_19]: Councilor Malay?

1564
02:27:29,062 --> 02:27:29,142
[SPEAKER_19]: Yes.

1565
02:27:30,482 --> 02:27:31,343
[SPEAKER_19]: Councilor Scott Felly?

1566
02:27:31,443 --> 02:27:31,683
[SPEAKER_19]: Yes.

1567
02:27:32,783 --> 02:27:33,384
[SPEAKER_19]: Councilor Singh?

1568
02:27:33,424 --> 02:27:33,604
[SPEAKER_19]: Yes.

1569
02:27:34,544 --> 02:27:35,345
[SPEAKER_19]: Vice President Lazaro?

1570
02:27:35,365 --> 02:27:35,425
[SPEAKER_19]: Yes.

1571
02:27:36,365 --> 02:27:37,106
[SPEAKER_19]: And President Pierce?

1572
02:27:37,546 --> 02:27:37,806
[SPEAKER_07]: Yes.

1573
02:27:37,826 --> 02:27:39,047
[SPEAKER_07]: I have an affirmative, none of the negative.

1574
02:27:39,067 --> 02:27:41,208
[SPEAKER_07]: The motion passes.

1575
02:27:41,228 --> 02:27:48,091
[SPEAKER_07]: 26-122, submitted by Mayor Marina Lungokern, Community Preservation Committee, appropriation request, Royal House and Shiloh Baptist Church.

1576
02:27:48,791 --> 02:27:52,733
[SPEAKER_07]: I do want to note that there was a fishing,

1577
02:27:54,764 --> 02:28:08,969
[SPEAKER_07]: scam that did go out essentially using my name and some random email to folks who had received CPA funds being like you're on the city council agenda please pay us money.

