[SPEAKER_07]: Seeing none, is there a motion?

1744
02:42:06,668 --> 02:42:09,009
[SPEAKER_07]: Oh, on the motion approved by Vice President Lazaro, seconded by?

1745
02:42:10,750 --> 02:42:12,311
[SPEAKER_07]: Seconded by Councilor Callahan.

1746
02:42:12,891 --> 02:42:13,252
[SPEAKER_07]: Thank you.

1747
