[SPEAKER_19]: Councilor Kelly?

1749
02:42:18,818 --> 02:42:18,978
[SPEAKER_19]: Yes.

1750
02:42:20,139 --> 02:42:20,879
[SPEAKER_19]: Councilor Lemming?

1751
02:42:22,380 --> 02:42:22,700
[SPEAKER_20]: Yes.

1752
02:42:24,081 --> 02:42:24,721
[SPEAKER_19]: Councilor Maloney?

1753
02:42:24,741 --> 02:42:25,882
[SPEAKER_19]: Yes.

